0.2.0  2026-05-29

  - Added hidden artifacts placed inside the stronghold.
  - Added stamina restoration when an artifact is found.
  - Added artifact messages to the game status output.
  - Added debug rendering for artifact positions.
  - Added STRONGHOLD_DEBUG_SHOW_ARTIFACTS debug option.
  - Documented debug options in README.
  - Improved highlighting of status values in terminal output.
  